Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,椿辉红羽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是来自断绝之壁的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你的爱意是真心？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是真心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只要在法庭上得到他们的百合承认
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,熊就能变成女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是要想得到百合承认就必须舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,自己最珍贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这只是露露的猜测
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那时的银子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是把从红红那里得到的爱意舍弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你说错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,为了实现愿望而舍弃爱意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是银子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,百合裁判就此开庭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,被告人 椿辉红羽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你有要申述的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我想永远和银子在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以求求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,请将银子变成人类的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,裁判长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,被告犯下了傲慢之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有罪 Guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,傲慢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,傲慢就是想要改变百合城银子身份的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是没办法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为熊是会被排除的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而且银子她成为人之后一定会更幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,呜哇 真有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,锃锃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才说你的想法是傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是傲慢也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,请将银子变成人类的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不过有一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须舍弃爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,简而言之 你会忘记银子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,梦醒时分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你就会拒绝她了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拒绝？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我许下了不能许下的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,误以为自己那一厢情愿的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,便是世间真理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那一刻终会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,透明风暴呼啸而至之时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你将会找到百合城银子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,倘若你和她再次成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,成功交换誓约之吻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就能永远在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,锃锃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那么被告人 椿辉红羽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,请回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你要让百合城银子成为人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抑或 你要放弃爱意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会放弃爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,请将银子变成人类的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我以最珍贵的东西为代价
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,许下了想让银子成为人类的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,百合裁判就此开庭
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,被告人 椿辉红羽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你承认自己的罪行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我承认
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经犯下了傲慢之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,许下了想让银子成为人类女孩子的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 在透明风暴之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到自己的所求了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.32,Text1,,0,0,150,,{\fad(450,0)}回 忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,教给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的所求——真爱找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,纯花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不再害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,只要不忘记爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就永远不会孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,只要不放弃爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,即使有所失却
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会变得透明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要纵身坠入风暴之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这… 这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,露露 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把这颗星星…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,把真正的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,交给银子的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:12:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你才不是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷呜嗷呜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我是食人熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,独孤求爱的银子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来吃你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快点开枪打死我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我就要把大家全吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我是罪熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷呜嗷呜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,银子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,红羽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,终于 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,熊利亚大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 熊利亚大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要恢复真身了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我们也该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是Sexy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,吓啵嗒～嘟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真是Cool
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,锃锃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:56.04,Text1,,38,0,203,,{\fad(350,0)}熊利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:56.04,Text2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)}{\pos(1119,1009.5)\fsp0\fscx110}爱之星
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.68,0:14:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,椿辉红羽
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.75,0:14:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你的爱意 是真心？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:14:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是真心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,…打碎我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,熊利亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,请您将我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,变成熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,百合 承认
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这… 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,红羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,银子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你始终不忘记爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你始终不放弃爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,让我给你… 誓约之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:17:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从今以后永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷呜嗷呜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,百合 承认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,超… 超不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,人竟然变成了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,多么…可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们 已经不能开炮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你… 你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那已经不是人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是熊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,恶必须排除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,别犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,别思考
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,开枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们的齐心协力之下终于做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们成功地排除了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,蔓延在这所学园里的可怕的恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,到头来我们还是必须成为透明的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 让我们开始排除仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友 是重于一切的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,此刻在这里的朋友 就是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.71,Text1,,0,0,150,,回 忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,开枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,无法融入我们的人是在给我们添麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这种不合群的人就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 让我们决定下一个需要排除的恶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,下…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:08.62,Text2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1432,814)\frz39}故\N障
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,下作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,下作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,找到你了
