Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,实现了誓约之吻的两人
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.54,0:21:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在「爱之星」的指引下
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.71,0:21:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,跨越断绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,踏上了新的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 姐家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她们两人 最后怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,米伦觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯～ 我不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有一件事我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.09,0:22:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,亲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.66,0:22:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,誓约之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就由我来亲好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,米伦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.74,0:22:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,永远在一起哦
